The paper deals with optimization problems related to graph cuts and labeling, which are typically studied in the areas of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational geometry (cs.CG), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of submodular and supermodular functions is also a common theme in these areas.
